        <p>Football is a team sport played between two teams of <mark>eleven players</mark> with a <strong>spherical ball</strong>. It is the most<stromg>popular sport</stromg>  in the world.</p >
    <h2>Cricket</h2> 
    <p>Cricket is a <strong>bat-and-ball</strong> game played between two teams of <mark>eleven players</mark> on a field at the center of which is a <mark>22-yard (20-meter)</mark> pitch with a wicket at each end, each comprising two bails balanced on three stumps.</p>
